---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import CTABlock from '../components/CTABlock.astro';
export const prerender = true;
---

<Layout
  title="Partner Program — Fast Web Guru | Wholesale Web Infrastructure for Agencies"
  description="Marketers, designers, and agencies: earn wholesale margin on every client you bring to Fast Web Guru. We handle all infrastructure and support. You keep the relationship."
>
  <section class="section-dark py-20 lg:py-28">
    <div class="container max-w-3xl">
      <h1 class="text-white mb-6">Build a real income reselling the web infrastructure Australian businesses actually need.</h1>
      <p class="text-zinc-400 text-xl leading-relaxed">If you're a marketer, copywriter, designer, or agency — and you're tired of managing client websites that don't pay you properly — there's a conversation worth having.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section-warm py-16">
    <div class="container max-w-3xl">
      <h2 class="mb-6">The straight version</h2>
      <div class="space-y-4 text-brand-text-secondary text-lg leading-relaxed">
        <p>Most agencies and freelancers spend enormous time managing client websites. Chasing developers. Fielding hosting complaints at inconvenient hours. Doing the infrastructure work that's necessary but nobody pays for properly.</p>
        <p>Fast Web Guru fixes that. We're the infrastructure and the support team. You're the relationship.</p>
        <p>We handle everything once your client is on board — hosting, updates, AI tools, Workflow Hub, support person. Your client gets a better service than most agencies can deliver at double the price. You earn wholesale margin on every one of them, every month.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section-light section-pad">
    <div class="container max-w-3xl">
      <h2 class="mb-12">How it works</h2>
      <div class="space-y-10">
        {[
          {
            title: 'Bring your clients onto Fast Web Guru',
            body: 'We handle everything: hosting, updates, AI tools, support. Your clients get same-day website updates, a real support person, and one fixed monthly price.',
          },
          {
            title: 'Earn wholesale margin on every active client',
            body: 'True partners, no time-limited payouts or once off affiliate fees, you get a generous monthly wholesale margin. Ongoing, as long as the clients stay active, building our businesses together is the Fast Web Guru way.',
          },
          {
            title: 'Keep the client relationship',
            body: 'You\'re not handing your clients to us. Fast Web Guru is the engine. You\'re the front door. Your clients are your clients.',
          },
        ].map((item, i) => (
          <div class="flex gap-6 pb-10 border-b border-brand-border last:border-0">
            <div class="step-number flex-shrink-0 w-16">{i + 1}</div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-bold text-xl mb-3">{item.title}</h3>
              <p class="text-brand-text-secondary text-lg leading-relaxed">{item.body}</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section-mid py-16">
    <div class="container max-w-3xl">
      <h2 class="mb-4">You're not working for us. You're using us.</h2>
      <div class="space-y-4 text-brand-text-secondary text-lg leading-relaxed">
        <p>Fast Web Guru Advocates are self-employed. Your loyalty is to your clients, not to us. We're the infrastructure, the support team, and the wholesale engine behind your business.</p>
        <p>Some Advocates use the Red Envelope* campaign — a personalised, locally-rooted outreach approach that creates genuine curiosity without a single sales pitch. We'll explain it when you get in touch.</p>
        <p>You'll also get access to your own Fast Web Guru plan — so you run your own business on the same platform your clients use, and you can speak about it from actual experience.</p>
        <p class="text-sm italic text-brand-text-secondary/70">*Red Letter Days have special meaning at Fast Web Guru — ask us why…</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section-light py-16">
    <div class="container max-w-3xl">
      <h2 class="mb-8">Who's a good fit</h2>
      <ul class="space-y-4 list-none p-0">
        {[
          'Digital marketers who keep getting asked "can you sort my website?"',
          'Copywriters and designers whose clients need ongoing web support',
          'Web developers who want a white-label hosting and management solution',
          'Systems integrators looking for a reliable AI-capable platform to resell',
          'Anyone building a local network — especially in Hunter Valley, Newcastle, Sydney, Melbourne, or Yarra Valley',
        ].map(item => (
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-lg">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-brand-accent flex-shrink-0 mt-1" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M4.5 12.75l6 6 9-13.5"/></svg>
            <span class="text-brand-text-secondary">{item}</span>
          </li>
        ))}
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Final CTA -->
  <section class="section-dark py-16">
    <div class="container max-w-2xl text-center">
      <h2 class="text-white mb-4">Interested?<br>Let's talk directly.</h2>
      <p class="text-zinc-400 text-lg mb-8">No lengthy application.<br>Just a straight conversation about whether it's a fit.</p>
      <a href="/contact" class="btn-primary text-base py-4 px-10">Get in touch about the partner program →</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
